Final Comparison\par
Requirement\tab S3\tab Azure Blob\tab Winner\par
Hot/Cool/Archive tagging\tab Good\tab Excellent\tab Azure Blob\par
Query by tag\tab Limited\tab Native\tab Azure Blob\par
Frequent profile reads/writes\tab Poor\tab Poor\tab Neither\par
Append activity logs\tab No native append\tab Append Blob\tab Azure Blob\par
